-- Lazard names Steven Golub as interim CEO
-- 
-- Wed Oct 14, 2009 7:28pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/10/14/us-lazard-brief-idUSTRE59D64X20091014

 

 (Reuters) - Lazard Ltd has named Steven J. Golub, the company's vice chairman, as interim chief after the death of Bruce Wasserstein, it said on Wednesday. 

 The company said the appointment is effective immediately.